title: Uptown - Testimony (Korean Hip-Hop 2006)
description:
Uptown was first formed in Korea in 1996 from a group of Korean-Americans and disbanded in 2000 after their 7th album.  This is their 2006 Comeback album, Testimony.  Enjoy!

For the video single from this album, check out "My Style" on Youtube.

1. My Style
2. Fiesta
3. [Korean]
4. One Mo' Time
5. Amigo
6. Ola
7. [Korean]
8. Karma
9. No Mo' Cry
10. One Mo' Time (Remix)
11. My Style (English Version)

All tagged up and ready for your iPod or MP3 Player.  Tracks marked as [Korean] are named in Korean properly but will not display here correctly.  You should probably have East Asian language support installed on your system if you want to edit the tags.
